item.title: CVE-2024-34577|2024-08-30T14:24:50.094Z -- elecom%20co.%2Cltd. -- wrc-x3000gs2-b
item.description: Cross-site scripting vulnerability exists in WRC-X3000GS2-B, WRC-X3000GS2-W, and WRC-X3000GS2A-B due to improper processing of input values in easysetup.cgi. If a user views a malicious web page while logged in to the product, an arbitrary script may be executed on the user's web browser.
